modDescription:
This mod adds a Marauder monster [car](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-car-mods/). Requires Grease Monkey 5.

## Changelog

* **_(new)_** Fixed Marauder storage size error.
* Added new engine/horn sounds.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A19/tree/master/Marauder)** for A19  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A18/tree/master/Marauder)** for A18
